{"tid":2081986,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果：物流署採購既5,700萬個口罩 其中一批嫌違反《商品說明條例》 海關拘捕四人","createTime":"2020-06-27T16:01:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T03:52:59.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d6c2fdc425558f46baa645d566290297e4382f11","tid":2081986,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:01:51.000Z","msg":"年初武漢肺炎肆虐，市民四出奔走排隊撲罩，惟政府沿用「價低者得」方式招標，被批反應遲緩、離地。而直到2月尾，政府物流服務署方完成招標採購5,700萬個口罩。但周六（27日）深夜政府公佈，一批3月購入的口罩，部份涉嫌違反《商品說明條例》。有傳媒則報道指，海關已拘捕4人及搜查2間相關公司。<br />\n<br />\n政府物流署購入的口罩只會分發予醫護、從事隔離措施人員、政治清潔工及院舍職員等，而各部門則可以自行採購口罩，只要定單為1,000萬以下，就能毋須政策局批准直接採購，未知今次涉事口罩是否已分發予相關部門。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200627/IXETOKDP66HD4OOY7ZBBVDFFAY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200627%2FIXETOKDP66HD4OOY7ZBBVDFFAY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFiDm%2BQAENn3DIwfZikXBReQ%3D&h=e74bc6fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200627%2FIXETOKDP66HD4OOY7ZBBVDFFAY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=72435f3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200627/IXETOKDP66HD4OOY7ZBBVDFFAY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"7cb5a6541ddf94caf7df129d328b681f7997d549","tid":2081986,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T16:05:11.000Z","msg":"中圈套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58bc573ff243b4386cccc77141d41cccaa7557d4","tid":2081986,"uid":32150,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-